steps.html_instructions: Head east on E Myrtle St toward S 5th St
Turn right onto S 5th St

S 5th St turns slightly left and becomes I-55BUS S/S 6th St
Continue to follow I-55BUS S
Merge onto I-55 S

Keep left at the fork to stay on I-55 S
Entering Missouri
Take exit 40B for Interstate 55 S toward Interstate 44 W
Merge onto I-44/I-55 S
Keep left at the fork to continue on I-55 S, follow signs for Interstate 55 S
Take exit 174B to merge onto US-67 S toward Bonne Terre/Farmington
Take the US-67 S ramp to Corning Ar

Continue onto US-67 S
Entering Arkansas

Turn right onto US-62 W/US-67 S/W Main St
Continue to follow US-62 W/US-67 S

Slight left onto AR-90 E/US-67 S
Continue to follow US-67 S
Exit onto US-63 N/US-67 S toward Newport/Hardy/Little Rock
Slight right onto the US-67 S ramp to US-67 Spur N/Hoxie/Walnut Ridge/Newport

Continue onto US-67 S/SW Texas St
Continue to follow US-67 S
Continue onto AR-367 S
Turn left onto Air Base Rd
Turn right to merge onto US-67 S
Merge onto I-40 W/US-67 S
Keep left at the fork to continue on I-30 W
Take exit 139B for I-630
Continue onto I-630 W
Take exit 2B for Doctor Martin Luther King Junior Drive

Turn right onto Dr Martin Luther King Dr/M L King (signs for State Capitol Complex)
Continue to follow Dr Martin Luther King Dr
Turn left onto W 7th St
Turn right onto State Capitol
Slight right to stay on State Capitol

routes.summary: I-55 S, US-67 S and US-67 S
